flowRoot.flowPara: At any time, for any piece of the nearshore, we can ask where the drifters currently present originated, and infer the composition of the nearshore water column, tributary origin wise.
During the season we can track hundreds or thousands of virtual "drifters" (agents) from their source tributaries as they move around the lake.
What's the source of water in the nearshore?
Nutrient loads from up and down the shore.
